Baltic Sea? A Saltwater Pike???  Yep.  Biggest pike in the world come from there. They stay in the brackish areas during the winter but in warmer water will actually head into the ocean proper.

http://www.esoxhunter.com/SaltyPike.php   http://www.greysfishing.com/en-gb/news-and-events/news/uncategorised/saltwater-pike-in-europe/  Years ago I saw an article on fish scents, in the article it stated that pike showed a preference for mackerel scent, that might explain it?
Salt water pike, who would have thought.
